# Cloud Operations

The Cloud Operations team is a sub-group of some senior infrastructure engineers from the Technology Operations team. This team is responsible for managing and maintaining 
applications on public cloud. Currently most applications that this team is managing are on AWS.

Please see [our products](/#our-products) to find a list of applications we are currently responsible for.

## Who is this for?

This documentation is for anyone interested in the Cloud Operations team and its core values; for users of the applications managed by this team; and for the team.

